1
00:00:08,337 --> 00:00:11,888
Byiza, Murakaza neza nanone muri 4.6
Ibi byerekeye gucunga neza amafaranga

2
00:00:12,751 --> 00:00:15,969
Turaza kwibanda
kungorane z'ingenzi zo kuba ufite amafaranga cashi

3
00:00:16,610 --> 00:00:18,319
Mubyukuri, hari 
Icyibazo cyimwe cy'ingenzi,

4
00:00:18,319 --> 00:00:20,139
kitari ukuba ufite adahagije.

5
00:00:20,139 --> 00:00:23,603
Ikibazo cyonyine ni, ni gute
Udafite aguhagije?

6
00:00:23,603 --> 00:00:25,141
Ese usesagura ayo ufite?

7
00:00:25,141 --> 00:00:26,776
Ese abantu barayakwiba, n'ibindi.

8
00:00:26,776 --> 00:00:28,721
Turaza kuvuga muri macye
kubyerekye "ikigero ukoreshaho igishoro cyawe",

9
00:00:28,721 --> 00:00:30,692
Ibi tukaba twarabivuzeho mucyumweru cyashize,

10
00:00:30,692 --> 00:00:34,774
Uburyo wagicunga neza, kandi ukakigumisha hasi

11
00:00:34,774 --> 00:00:37,922
Turaaza kuvuga
kumoko ya konti atandukanye,

12
00:00:37,922 --> 00:00:40,251
n'impamvu ukeneye,
kujyira ama konti yawe akaba atandukanye.

13
00:00:40,251 --> 00:00:42,903
Turaganira kubijyanye n'amabanki,
n'icyo ukwiye gushaka muri banki

14
00:00:42,903 --> 00:00:46,830
Turaza gusoreza,
no kubindi bisubizo bitari ibyo muri banki

15
00:00:47,223 --> 00:00:50,285
Harimo n'uburyo bwo kwishyura ukoresheje ikoranabuhanga

16
00:00:50,285 --> 00:00:53,970
Kujyirango abantu birinde kujyendana,
amafaranga menshi.

17
00:00:54,019 --> 00:00:57,017
Reka rero tuganire,
Kukintu cyo gusesagura ho gatoya

18
00:00:57,017 --> 00:01:01,977
Reka tubihe ubusobanuro,
bwumvikana neza kurushaho,

19
00:01:01,977 --> 00:01:03,934
Icyo ukeneye gukor wowe ni ukureba.

20
00:01:03,934 --> 00:01:08,426
Kuburyo amafaranga yinjira
n'uburyo asohoka.

21
00:01:09,649 --> 00:01:12,258
Ubu kugirango dukore uyu mwitozo,
Ndabasaba,

22
00:01:12,258 --> 00:01:15,022
Ko twirengajyira gatoya iby'icungamari bindi,

23
00:01:15,022 --> 00:01:16,852
Ibyo bisobanuye iki?

24
00:01:16,852 --> 00:01:18,422
Iyo utanze icyintu--

25
00:01:18,422 --> 00:01:21,383
Reka wenda tuvuge ko washakaga
kugura indi mudasobwa,

26
00:01:21,703 --> 00:01:25,137
Wenda tuvuge ko igura amadorari 1000--
hari uburyo bwinshi butandukanye

27
00:01:25,137 --> 00:01:29,014
bwo gutekereza,
ukuntu ayo mafaranga ari gutangwa.

28
00:01:29,014 --> 00:01:30,922
Ese uzajya wishyura mubyiciro,

29
00:01:30,922 --> 00:01:34,274
Mujyihe runaka,
mumyaka runaka?

30
00:01:34,914 --> 00:01:38,205
Ese uko igihe gishira cyigenda gitakaza agaciro? n'ibindi.

31
00:01:38,306 --> 00:01:42,912
Icyingenzi turi kurebaho uyu munsi ni,

32
00:01:43,252 --> 00:01:46,503
Biragutwara amafaranga angahe cashi
Kujyirango ugure iyo mudasobwa.

33
00:01:46,503 --> 00:01:49,415
Niba wari ufite amadorali 1000 kuri konti

34
00:01:49,415 --> 00:01:50,947
ugatanga 1000 cy'amadorali kuri mudasobwa,

35
00:01:50,947 --> 00:01:53,893
Ubu usigaye ntafaranga na rimwe ufite
kuri konti yawe, sibyo?

36
00:01:53,893 --> 00:01:55,360
Icyo nicyo turi kuvugaho,
tuvuga kuburyo amafaranga yinjira

37
00:01:55,360 --> 00:01:56,939
Ubu wenda umuntu yakwishyuye $100

38
00:01:56,939 --> 00:01:58,319
Kuberako yari akurimo ideni
rya $100 kubera impamvu runaka yindi.

39
00:01:58,319 --> 00:02:01,099
ubu ukaba ufite $100 kuri konti

40
00:02:01,099 --> 00:02:02,954
Iyi niyo mpamvu y'uyu mwitozo:

41
00:02:02,954 --> 00:02:06,311
Turi kureba uburyo amafaranga yinjira
n'uburyo asohoka,

42
00:02:06,311 --> 00:02:09,214
Tutitaye kuhantu yajyiye aturuka.

43
00:02:09,214 --> 00:02:12,354
Cyangwa niba yo mafaranga uyabara
nk'inyungu cyangwa igihombo cyangwa ikindi icyo ari cyo cyose

44
00:02:12,354 --> 00:02:16,596
Turi kwirebera gusa kumafaranga
yasohotse n'ayinjiye.

45
00:02:17,244 --> 00:02:19,038
Turabyumva?
Rero mugutangira--

46
00:02:19,038 --> 00:02:20,933
Nk'uko twabivuzeho
inshuro nyinshi--

47
00:02:20,933 --> 00:02:24,709
Usohora amafaranga kenshi
aruta ayo uri kwijiza.

48
00:02:25,231 --> 00:02:28,832
kandi icyinyuranyo cyiri hagati
y'ayo wasohoye

49
00:02:28,832 --> 00:02:33,596
N'ayo winjije,
ncyo twita "icyigero dukoreshaho igishoro"

50
00:02:33,596 --> 00:02:36,136
abandi nababyita
"iicyigero dukoreshaho igishoro ukuyemo ayo twinjiza"

51
00:02:36,136 --> 00:02:41,029
Kujyirango babitandukanye,
n'igiteranyo cy'amafaranga asohoka,

52
00:02:42,469 --> 00:02:45,208
bishobora kwitwa icyigero dukoreshaho amafaranga muri rusange

53
00:02:45,498 --> 00:02:47,861
Rero niba tureba ingano
y'amafaranga turi gusohora buri kwezi,

54
00:02:47,861 --> 00:02:51,285
Reka tuvuge, ko mugihe cy'ukwezi,
icyo tuzacyita "icyigero dukoreshaho amafaranga muri rusange",

55
00:02:51,285 --> 00:02:55,019
Hanyuma, niba koko
hari amafaranga turi kwinjiza,

56
00:02:55,019 --> 00:02:59,302
Tukaba twayakuramo
mumafaranga turi gusohora

57
00:02:59,302 --> 00:03:01,512
Kandi icyo cyaba icyigero dukoreshaho amafaranga ukuyemo ayinjiye

58
00:03:01,932 --> 00:03:04,115
Kuki se twashaka gukora uyu mwitozo?

59
00:03:04,115 --> 00:03:06,557
Kuko dukoresha,
 icyi cyigero ngo tubashe kumenya

60
00:03:06,557 --> 00:03:09,850
Ni igihe cyingana gute gisigaye
ngo amafaranga abe adushiranye?

61
00:03:09,850 --> 00:03:12,454
icyo cyikitwa "igihe amafaranga adushiranye"

62
00:03:12,454 --> 00:03:15,657
Niba rero ufite umubare  runaka,
w'amafaranga muri banki,

63
00:03:15,657 --> 00:03:20,186
Ukaba ufite n'icyigero ukoreshaho igishoro,
wagaba cyimwe icyindi

64
00:03:20,186 --> 00:03:22,200
Ukabasha kumenya
igihe runaka usigaranye

65
00:03:22,200 --> 00:03:23,679
mbere y'uko amafaranga agushirana.

66
00:03:25,000 --> 00:03:29,059
Reka dusubire kw'ifoto 
twabonye muri 4.1

67
00:03:29,059 --> 00:03:31,981
Igihe twarimo kuvuga,
Kungano y'amafaranga dukeneye

68
00:03:31,981 --> 00:03:36,032
Icyo gihe byari bigamije gukusanza amafaranga
ariko ubu tugiye kubikoresha

69
00:03:36,032 --> 00:03:38,557
Dutekereze kukigero dukoreshaho igishoro

70
00:03:39,269 --> 00:03:42,040
nk'uko muri kubibona kujyishushanyo hano,

71
00:03:42,040 --> 00:03:45,695
Dufite imyaka kumurongo uzamuka,

72
00:03:49,168 --> 00:03:53,648
Hanyuma hasi tukajyira amafaranga twinjiza.

73
00:03:54,038 --> 00:03:58,528
Amafaranga bidutwara, inyungu, n'uburyo amafaranga 
agenda aza mubihe bitandukanye

74
00:03:58,528 --> 00:04:00,543
Nanone ntago turi bwite cyane

75
00:04:00,543 --> 00:04:03,550
Kucyo  bisobanuye mu icungamari cyane,
iby'inyungu n'igihombo hano.

76
00:04:03,550 --> 00:04:07,394
Turaza kureba gusa,
kuburyo amafaranga yinjira anasohoka.

77
00:04:07,994 --> 00:04:13,385
Kandi nk'uko mushobora kuba mubibona,
mumwaka wambere, ntamafaranga yinjiye.

78
00:04:13,385 --> 00:04:16,277
Mumwaka wa kabiri dufite $50

79
00:04:16,277 --> 00:04:19,826
Tugakomeza gutanga
$100, $110, $120, $130, $140.

80
00:04:19,826 --> 00:04:22,949
Burigihe tuba dufite amafaranga twatanze, ni uko nyuma

81
00:04:22,949 --> 00:04:25,358
Tukajya tubona n;amafaranga yinjira agenda yiyongera,

82
00:04:25,358 --> 00:04:30,725
Bikarangira
Duhombye $100 mumwaka wa mbere,

83
00:04:31,595 --> 00:04:33,871
Ibyo bikajyira ingaruka no ku gihe gikurikiyeho

84
00:04:33,871 --> 00:04:37,136
yo kuba tuburaho $100 kumafaranga twatangiranye.

85
00:04:37,136 --> 00:04:38,718
Kumpera z'umwaka wa mbere

86
00:04:38,718 --> 00:04:44,543
Ubu rero icyo tugiye gukora,
Ni ukwitegereza muwaka wa kabiri,

87
00:04:44,543 --> 00:04:49,459
Uko aya mafaranga
ari kugenda muwaka wa kabiri,

88
00:04:51,122 --> 00:04:53,886
Mumwaka wa kabiri, dufite
$50 mumafaranga yinjira

89
00:04:53,886 --> 00:04:56,871
hanyuma tukagira amafaranga twatanze hanze angana na $110

90
00:04:57,391 --> 00:05:03,702
Ubwo rero kujyiye kuba,
$60 agabanutseho kumpera z'umwaka wa kabiri

91
00:05:03,702 --> 00:05:06,204
ujyereranije n'impera z'umwaka wa mbere

92
00:05:06,204 --> 00:05:07,978
Reka dutekereze,
twibaze akandi kantu kamwe.

93
00:05:07,978 --> 00:05:11,447
Tuvuge ko twatangiye,
uyu mwitozo wose

94
00:05:11,447 --> 00:05:14,194
dufite $150 kuri banki

95
00:05:14,794 --> 00:05:20,394
Twabonye ko kandi,
muwaka wa mbere hari havuyeho $100

96
00:05:20,394 --> 00:05:24,240
Niba rero twatangiranye $150,
Bizarangira,

97
00:05:24,240 --> 00:05:28,259
Dufite $50 gusa kumpera,
z'umwaka wa mbere.

98
00:05:32,732 --> 00:05:35,573
Nitwitegereza mubyo twinjije mumwaka wa kabiri,

99
00:05:36,605 --> 00:05:38,663
Wabona ko,
Tuzinjiza $50,

100
00:05:38,663 --> 00:05:42,427
Akaba aruta ho gacyaya $4 ku kwezi.

101
00:05:43,599 --> 00:05:48,823
Hanyuma, nitureba
Kuyo twatanze hanze, ni $110,

102
00:05:48,823 --> 00:05:51,581
Aruta ho gacye
$9 kukwezi

103
00:06:00,680 --> 00:06:03,593
Ariko twavugako icyigero dukoreshaho igishoro muri rusange

104
00:06:03,973 --> 00:06:07,492
yarutagaho gacye $9 kukwezi

105
00:06:08,386 --> 00:06:10,358
Ubu, icyigero dukoreshaho amafaranga ukuyemo ayinjiye

106
00:06:10,358 --> 00:06:15,565
cyangwa icyo abenshi bakwita
icyigero dukoreshaho igishoro, ni $5 kukwezi

107
00:06:19,562 --> 00:06:21,546
Hanyuma rero icyo tuzakora

108
00:06:21,546 --> 00:06:24,288
Tuzareba umubare w' amafaranga 
dufite mu ntoki

109
00:06:24,948 --> 00:06:28,196
Mu mpera z'umwaka
dutangiye uwa kabiri,

110
00:06:28,196 --> 00:06:31,544
Tubone ko dufite $50

111
00:06:31,544 --> 00:06:36,208
Tukaba tujyiye gukoresha,
icyigero, cya $5 kukwezi.

112
00:06:36,208 --> 00:06:40,754
Bisobanuye ko dufite amezi icumi gusa,
amafaranga akaba aradushiranye.

113
00:06:45,803 --> 00:06:49,384
Reka dutekereze noneho,
Impamvu icyi cyigero dukoreshaho amafaranga ari ingirakamaro

114
00:06:49,910 --> 00:06:55,386
birumvikana, iyo uzi igihe amafaranga azaba ashiriye
bituma biguha icyigereranyo

115
00:06:55,386 --> 00:06:58,461
cy'igihe runaka gisigaye ukomeje

116
00:06:58,461 --> 00:07:02,499
n'ibikorwa byawe bisanzwe
ukomerejeho nk'aho ntacyabaye

117
00:07:02,499 --> 00:07:05,029
ntihajyire na cyimwe uhindura,
ukinjiza amafaranga gusa

118
00:07:05,029 --> 00:07:06,282
wateganyaga kwinjiza

119
00:07:06,282 --> 00:07:08,212
kandi ugasohora amafaranga
wateganyije gusohora,

120
00:07:08,212 --> 00:07:12,161
ukanareba ayo ufite muri banki,
ibyo bikaguha

121
00:07:12,961 --> 00:07:15,262
akantu k'akagereranyo
k'uko igihe runaka cyingana

122
00:07:15,262 --> 00:07:17,843
waba ugumye byibuze mu ishoramari ryawe.

123
00:07:18,313 --> 00:07:20,104
Yego, navuga ko bigufasha

124
00:07:20,104 --> 00:07:22,200
Uri kwibaza
kuburyo uzagura ibikorwa

125
00:07:22,200 --> 00:07:26,762
kuberako rimwe na rimwe,
dukenera guhara amafaranga

126
00:07:26,762 --> 00:07:29,364
kujyirengo turebe ko twazaguka muminsi iri imbere

127
00:07:29,364 --> 00:07:32,313
Twavuze ho gato,
kubijyanye no kwagura ishoramari ryawe

128
00:07:33,033 --> 00:07:37,292
mucyumweru gishize, kandi nabyo byagufasha,
mukubitekerazaho, sibyo?

129
00:07:37,292 --> 00:07:40,263
niba uziko ufite
 igihe cyinini mbere y'uko amafaranga agushirana

130
00:07:41,023 --> 00:07:43,224
kandi icyigero ukoreshaho igishoro cyikaba cyiri hasi

131
00:07:43,224 --> 00:07:47,536
ubwo washaka kujyira icyo ukora

132
00:07:47,536 --> 00:07:51,434
cyashobora kukuzanira,
ubushobozi bwo kwagura ubucuruzi bwawe

133
00:07:51,434 --> 00:07:53,835
Ukajyira amahirwe menshi yo gukura mu ishoramari

134
00:07:53,835 --> 00:07:56,282
niba utekereza ko uri gukoresha igishoro vuba vuba,

135
00:07:56,282 --> 00:08:00,366
Ushobora gukenera kubigabanya,
ho gatoya bishobora nabyo kukubera imbogamizi,

136
00:08:00,366 --> 00:08:04,217
mu bihe bimwe na bimwe ejo hazaza,
mukuba wakwagura ubucuruzi.

137
00:08:04,397 --> 00:08:06,066
Biterwa
n'ibikorwa remezo bishorwamo amafaranga

138
00:08:06,066 --> 00:08:09,942
ukeneye gukora,
kujyirango ubone uko wagura ubucuruzi bwawe.

139
00:08:11,042 --> 00:08:16,469
None. ni igihe cyingana gute ugomba kuba ufite
mbere y'uko amafaranga agushirana?

140
00:08:17,087 --> 00:08:21,639
Abantu benshi bavuga,
ko ukwye gutangira kujyira impungenge

141
00:08:21,639 --> 00:08:24,596
iyo ufite igihe cyiri munsi y'amezi atandatu,

142
00:08:24,596 --> 00:08:27,273
Ko hari ibyo ucyeneye,
guhita ugabanya ako kanya,

143
00:08:27,273 --> 00:08:29,584
ugatangira gushaka andi mafaranga.

144
00:08:29,584 --> 00:08:34,721
Rero ucyeneye kureba neza
hamwe cyangwa hose muri aho hatatu, sibyo?

145
00:08:34,721 --> 00:08:37,148
Uzi amafaranga yose
ari kuri konti,

146
00:08:37,148 --> 00:08:39,039
muri banki, cyangwa unayafite muntoki,

147
00:08:39,039 --> 00:08:42,754
hanyuma uzi,
amafaranga uri kwinjiza, 

148
00:08:42,754 --> 00:08:44,402
ukamenya n'amafaranga uri gusohora.

149
00:08:44,402 --> 00:08:49,380
ucyeneye rero  wenda kubaka,
ingano ukeneye gutangirana,

150
00:08:49,380 --> 00:08:53,529
ushaka ibikoresho, binyuze ugukusanya amafaranga,

151
00:08:53,529 --> 00:08:58,360
ukeneye kongera,
amafaranga yinjira, biciye mugucuruza,

152
00:08:59,120 --> 00:09:04,267
na, cyangwa ukeneye kugabanya
amafaranga usohora.

153
00:09:04,267 --> 00:09:06,329
Turaza kubivugaho muminota micye.

154
00:09:07,469 --> 00:09:10,282
Icyigero ukoreshaho igishoro kandi kigufasha,
muguteganya uko uzakusanya amafaranga,

155
00:09:10,282 --> 00:09:11,627
nk'uko nabivuze.

156
00:09:11,627 --> 00:09:15,517
Rero uratekerazako ushobora gukenera,
gukusanya amafaranga,

157
00:09:15,517 --> 00:09:17,389
Urimo uragenda ubura--

158
00:09:17,389 --> 00:09:19,629
Abantu bayita kubura aho wirukira"

159
00:09:20,069 --> 00:09:21,729
Ni nk'uko waba wururutse indege,

160
00:09:21,729 --> 00:09:26,497
Ukaba ubona ahantu hacye
hasigaye ho kwirukira imbere yawe,

161
00:09:26,497 --> 00:09:28,900
iyo utangiye kubura aho wirukira,
utangira kujyira impungenge.

162
00:09:28,900 --> 00:09:30,555
Bigufasha guteganya
uburyo uzakuzanya amafaranga mo gacye.

163
00:09:30,555 --> 00:09:32,713
"yee, nsigarannya umwaka umwe gusa,

164
00:09:32,713 --> 00:09:34,284
nkeneye gutangira kubitekerezaho nonaha.

165
00:09:34,284 --> 00:09:39,043
Kandi niba mwibuka,
kukintu cyo gukusanya amafaranga,

166
00:09:39,043 --> 00:09:40,577
Twagiye mubyo kugereranya

167
00:09:40,577 --> 00:09:46,306
Tureba n'amezi bitwara,
kujyirango ubone amafaranga runaka.

168
00:09:46,676 --> 00:09:48,657
Ibi rero buzagufasha mugupanga gahunda zawe.

169
00:09:48,657 --> 00:09:50,589
Kuko niba uziko,
usigaranya imyaka ibiri

170
00:09:50,589 --> 00:09:52,646
Ushobora gufata igihe cyirekire ho gato.

171
00:09:52,646 --> 00:09:56,807
ugashaka amafaranga,
ahantu azatinda kuza ho gato

172
00:09:56,807 --> 00:09:58,053
Naho ubundi waza gusanga ugomba gushaka gusa

173
00:09:58,053 --> 00:10:01,503
ahantu hava amafaranga ujyeranije
mujyihe gito

174
00:10:02,733 --> 00:10:06,935
Biha n'icyimenyetso abashoramari,
bakabona icyo uri gushaka.

175
00:10:07,410 --> 00:10:11,205
Urabizi ko uri gushaka,
icyintu cyatuma wagura ubucuruzi,

176
00:10:11,205 --> 00:10:13,893
Urashaka ikintu cyikwihutisha,
nka campanye yo kwamamaza

177
00:10:14,103 --> 00:10:16,822
Ndetse, n'ingano y'amafaranga ushaka,

178
00:10:16,822 --> 00:10:18,500
ujyereranije n'uburyo uyakoreshamo

179
00:10:18,500 --> 00:10:22,837
nabyo byaba icyimenyetso,
cy'ingezi kubashoramari.

180
00:10:24,343 --> 00:10:29,322
Hanyuma rero, icyigero ukoreshaho igishoro,
cyagaragaza ahari intege nke

181
00:10:29,322 --> 00:10:31,238
Muburyo ujyenda winjiza mo amafaranga.

182
00:10:31,238 --> 00:10:37,602
Rero niba ufite amafaranga winjiza,
aza rimwe na rimwe

183
00:10:39,712 --> 00:10:42,344
Hakajyira ikintu cyiba
hagati y'uyu munsi n'icyindi gihe

184
00:10:42,344 --> 00:10:47,127
amafaranga yari kuzazira,
bishobora kurangira uri mu buryo

185
00:10:47,127 --> 00:10:50,677
ushobora kumara amafaranga byihuse,
kurusha uko wabitekerezaga.

186
00:10:50,677 --> 00:10:54,268
Habaho rer integenke,
igihe amafaranga usohora atajya ahinduka--

187
00:10:54,268 --> 00:10:55,739
Ari nabyo bikunze kubaho,
kuko akenshi

188
00:10:55,739 --> 00:10:57,756
uba utanga amafaranga nk'imishahara.

189
00:10:57,756 --> 00:11:00,497
kandi amafaranga usohora adahinduka.

190
00:11:00,497 --> 00:11:02,407
Hanyuma uburyo amafaranga yawe bukaba butandukanye

191
00:11:02,407 --> 00:11:05,336
Buri gihe mugihe runaka
ese koko ubona amafaranga yinjira--

192
00:11:05,336 --> 00:11:07,515
Aho harimo akabazo,

193
00:11:07,515 --> 00:11:09,911
ko amafaranga ashobora kugushirana
mbere y'uko andi mafaranga aza.

194
00:11:09,911 --> 00:11:11,454
Reka turebe urugero rwabyo.

195
00:11:11,454 --> 00:11:14,412
Ibyo tujyiye gukora ni 
ukwitegereza mu mwaka wa kabiri

196
00:11:14,412 --> 00:11:16,342
duhereye kurugero twabonye, sibyo?

197
00:11:16,342 --> 00:11:19,806
ni ukuvuga ko tugifite $50 yinjiye,

198
00:11:19,806 --> 00:11:22,267
Ndetse turacyafite n'asohoka $110

199
00:11:22,267 --> 00:11:25,842
Tujyiye kubicamo ibice,
turebe ukwezi ku kwezi.

200
00:11:25,842 --> 00:11:28,637
Hanyuma twibuke ko twatangiye uyu mwaka
dufite $50 kuri banki

201
00:11:28,637 --> 00:11:31,019
Icyigaragara hano kurusha ibindi ni

202
00:11:31,019 --> 00:11:33,625
Ntahandi hantu ho gukura amafaranga dufite.

203
00:11:33,625 --> 00:11:37,371
Dufite amezi atandatu ntafaranga na rimwe twinjiza,

204
00:11:37,371 --> 00:11:42,123
Hanyuma, mukwezi kwa karindwi,
duteganya kubona $40

205
00:11:42,372 --> 00:11:45,491
Ariko abafaranga dusohora, asa n'aho adahinduka.

206
00:11:45,491 --> 00:11:47,889
Hari ibintu bibiri by'ingenzi
dufite mumwaka ujya kurangira,

207
00:11:47,889 --> 00:11:50,722
Ariko dufite $8 kukwezi
mujyihe cy'amezi umunani

208
00:11:51,542 --> 00:11:54,221
Tukajyira n'amafaranga dusohora y'inyongera
ya $15 mukwezi kwa munani

209
00:11:54,221 --> 00:11:55,771
Ubu ni ubitekerezaho,

210
00:11:55,771 --> 00:11:58,420
Ntago ari,
ahantu heza ho kuba, sibyo?

211
00:11:58,420 --> 00:12:01,336
Watangiranye $50
mu ntangiriro z'umwaka,

212
00:12:01,336 --> 00:12:05,802
None ubu ugiye gusohora
umunani inshuro esheshatu--

213
00:12:07,672 --> 00:12:12,271
Uraza gusohora $48
mbere y'uko ubona $40 yawe

214
00:12:12,811 --> 00:12:16,624
Hanyuma ukaba usigaranye $2
mu mpera z'ukwezi kwa gatandatu

215
00:12:17,964 --> 00:12:21,266
Hanyuma uzatangirana,
n'amafaranga asohoka mu kwezi kwa karindwi,

216
00:12:21,266 --> 00:12:24,586
Rero nihabaho gutinda,
kw'amafaranga yinjira,

217
00:12:24,946 --> 00:12:28,313
Amafaranga azagushirana,
mbere y'uko ubona andi.

218
00:12:28,639 --> 00:12:31,511
Ubukungu bugenze nabi
umuntu akanzura

219
00:12:31,511 --> 00:12:34,199
ko atagishaka kubikora--
cyangwa ari companyi

220
00:12:34,199 --> 00:12:37,019
niba wizeye ko uzabona amafaranga,
avuye muri companyi runaka, umukiriya ukomeye cyane,

221
00:12:37,019 --> 00:12:41,460
ibi nabyo bikwereka ko-- uri kugendera
kukintu runaka kiri aho

222
00:12:42,390 --> 00:12:44,080
kujyirango bigufashe gukomeza gukora.

223
00:12:44,080 --> 00:12:48,261
Ibi rero bikaba ari bihe bibi
byo kuba waba urimo, muri iki gihe.

224
00:12:48,261 --> 00:12:52,390
Hari amafaranga menshi azaza
azishyurira umwaka wose,

225
00:12:52,390 --> 00:12:54,978
igikomeye cyane, ukaba uyatezeho amakiriro

226
00:12:55,277 --> 00:13:00,612
none amafaranga giye kkugushirana
mbere y'amaezi atandatu,

227
00:13:00,612 --> 00:13:03,504
Cyangwa arindwi,
ayo mafaranga ni ataza.

228
00:13:04,187 --> 00:13:08,260
Reka tuvuge ku inyerezwa ry'umutungo.
Inyerezwa ry'umutungo ni iki?

229
00:13:09,552 --> 00:13:15,225
Inyerezwa ry'umutungo bikoresha akenshi,
iyo abantu bakwiba.

230
00:13:16,700 --> 00:13:21,132
Akenshi, tuvuga inyerezwa

231
00:13:21,132 --> 00:13:23,951
Iyo ari umuntu wo mukorana ukwiba.

232
00:13:24,548 --> 00:13:28,128
Ntago ari ngombwa cyane ko 
hari umntu uba akwiba--

233
00:13:28,128 --> 00:13:31,155
Ibyo turaza kubivugaho nyuma
byo kuba umuntu yakwiba n'ibindi 

234
00:13:31,155 --> 00:13:34,930
Ibyo turi kuvugaho ni nko kuba umuntu yatwara igicuruzwa

235
00:13:36,491 --> 00:13:38,743
mbere y'uko cyigira amahirwwe
yo kuba cyagezwa kumukiriya.

236
00:13:39,031 --> 00:13:40,438
gishobora kuba ari igicuruzwa kigaragara,

237
00:13:40,438 --> 00:13:43,445
Biri gukurwa
mu bubiko nyuma bikagurishwa.

238
00:13:43,445 --> 00:13:45,969
cyangwa bigakoreshwa murugo n'abakozi.

239
00:13:46,479 --> 00:13:48,904
Arko bishobora no kuvuga hafi y'ikintu cyose

240
00:13:48,904 --> 00:13:53,188
cyo kuba umuntu mukorana yatwara amafaranga,
cyangwa ikindi cyintu cyose cya companyi.

241
00:13:54,597 --> 00:13:58,019
Ibi bintu bikunze kuvugwaho,

242
00:13:59,089 --> 00:14:04,176
ariko turabyumva mubihuha-- wacyeka
umuntu mu ntangiriro

243
00:14:04,176 --> 00:14:09,118
Uba afite amahirwe menshi yo gutwara ibikoresho,
bya companyi?

244
00:14:09,118 --> 00:14:12,840
Ibi ntago bikora neza hano,
kubakoresha murandasi,

245
00:14:12,840 --> 00:14:16,503
Ariko reka ndebe
niba nabasha kubereka icyo ibi bivuze.

246
00:14:16,503 --> 00:14:18,180
Ibi muri kubibona?

247
00:14:18,520 --> 00:14:20,220
Oh, ibi ntago biri bukunde
kubera urumuri.

248
00:14:20,220 --> 00:14:22,398
Kandi byafashwe mbere!

249
00:14:23,089 --> 00:14:25,037
Ariko reba mu ndorerwamo.

250
00:14:25,887 --> 00:14:30,943
Muri rusange, umuntu ubwe,
uba ushobora gutwara ibikoresho bya companyi

251
00:14:30,943 --> 00:14:33,428
ni nyiri ukuyishinga we ubwe.

252
00:14:35,318 --> 00:14:41,944
Nyiri ukuyishinga aba yabasha kujyera,
by'umwihariko mubihe bibanza

253
00:14:41,944 --> 00:14:45,127
nyiri ugushinga companyi 
aba akora ku mafaranga

254
00:14:45,127 --> 00:14:47,265
ya companyi nk'uko yinjira,

255
00:14:47,265 --> 00:14:53,193
Ibyo bigatuma abantu batekereza
ko ba nyiri ugushinga ama companyi bafite amahirwe menshi

256
00:14:53,193 --> 00:14:58,607
yo kuba aribo ba mbere bacyekwa,
iyo haje ibintu byo kunyereza umutungo.

257
00:14:58,607 --> 00:15:03,678
Hanyuma n'ubujura, reka tuvuge 
kubujura teihuse.

258
00:15:03,678 --> 00:15:05,977
Bitewe n'ingano y'amafaranga
ufite mu ntoki,

259
00:15:05,977 --> 00:15:08,080
n'uburyo uyajyendana,

260
00:15:09,010 --> 00:15:13,077
Kuba bayakwiba, ni icyintu gikomeye

261
00:15:13,077 --> 00:15:15,533
mu buryo uteganya gucunga amafaranga.

262
00:15:16,854 --> 00:15:21,425
Ibaze baramutse bakwibye,
wari uri ugendana

263
00:15:21,425 --> 00:15:25,032
cyimwe cya kabiri cy'amafaranga uteganya
gukoresha umwaka utaha

264
00:15:25,600 --> 00:15:28,607
Hanyuma utekereze no kucyo ibyo bikora,
kugihe amafaranga azashirira--

265
00:15:28,607 --> 00:15:30,475
Ibyo biracyigabanya mo kabiri

266
00:15:30,475 --> 00:15:33,782
Rero ni ihurizo rikomeye,

267
00:15:33,782 --> 00:15:38,084
none tugiye gutekereza,
muminota micye igiye kuza,

268
00:15:38,084 --> 00:15:45,402
ni gute wagabanya kugendana amafaranga menshi?

269
00:15:46,815 --> 00:15:49,931
Birashukana,
turebye kubyo kunyereza umutungo--

270
00:15:49,931 --> 00:15:55,335
ni nabibi kumpamvu z'umutekano,
ibijyanye no kuba wakwibwa.

271
00:15:55,567 --> 00:16:01,086
Kandi nabwo kuyasiga ari menshi murugo--
nabyo ntibyizewe ijana ku ijana,

272
00:16:01,086 --> 00:16:03,985
Kuko no murugo bashobora kuhiba,

273
00:16:03,985 --> 00:16:05,812
Nawe ubwawe ushobora kwiyibisha 

274
00:16:05,812 --> 00:16:08,879
iyo uri ujyenda ugaruka
utwaye amafaranga.

275
00:16:08,879 --> 00:16:12,176
Muri rusange, niba hari ubundi buryo

276
00:16:12,176 --> 00:16:15,148
Butari ugutwara amafaranga,
menshi ngo uyagendane,

277
00:16:15,148 --> 00:16:16,911
nibwo wahitamo,

278
00:16:16,911 --> 00:16:18,556
Biturutse ku mpamvu zitandukanye.

279
00:16:18,556 --> 00:16:20,654
Reka dutekereze kukigero ukoreshaho igishoro.

280
00:16:20,654 --> 00:16:25,278
Ni iki twakora kigirango
icyi cyigero kiba kiri hasi?

281
00:16:25,963 --> 00:16:31,253
Mbere na mbere,
ukeneye kujyira gahunda.

282
00:16:32,250 --> 00:16:37,729
kujyira gahunnda bisobanuye byoroshye,
kujyira gahunda y'ukwezi n'umwaka,

283
00:16:37,729 --> 00:16:42,216
Ukajyira ibyo uteganya--
ukareba umwaka ushize,

284
00:16:42,926 --> 00:16:44,596
wasohoye amafaranga angahe?

285
00:16:44,596 --> 00:16:46,687
Winjije angahe?

286
00:16:46,687 --> 00:16:50,911
Hanyuma ugakora imibare
ukareba ikigero ukoreshaho igishoro mukwezi

287
00:16:50,911 --> 00:16:54,964
Hanyuma ugateganyiriza
uko bizaba bimeze mugihe cy'umwaka uzaza,

288
00:16:55,724 --> 00:16:59,737
Ayo uteganya kuzasohora

289
00:16:59,737 --> 00:17:02,018
n'ayo uteganya kuzinjiza

290
00:17:02,308 --> 00:17:06,935
Hanyuma ukanakora imibare
ukamenya igihe uzamara amafaranga ataragushirana.

291
00:17:07,836 --> 00:17:12,091
Ariko hejuru yo gutekereza no kucyigero  cy'amafaranga
ukoresha havuyemo ayinjiye,

292
00:17:12,091 --> 00:17:14,161
Tekereza no kukigero cy'amafaranga ukoresha muri rusange

293
00:17:14,161 --> 00:17:19,431
Ni hagera igihe 
cyo gutanga amafaranga menshi, jya wibaza,

294
00:17:19,431 --> 00:17:23,152
"Ese ibi koko ndabikeneye?
Aya mafaranga koko nkeneye kuyakoresha nonaha?

295
00:17:23,152 --> 00:17:25,371
Uzi, ubu nagerageza nkareba

296
00:17:25,371 --> 00:17:27,019
niba hari icyindi cyintu nakora?

297
00:17:27,019 --> 00:17:31,180
Ese nabasha gutegerezaho ikindi gihe,
Ibi nkazaba mbikora mu kwezi cyangwa abiri

298
00:17:31,180 --> 00:17:34,740
Nkatekereza niba
nabaho ntaguze icyi cyintu?"

299
00:17:36,080 --> 00:17:37,742
Ibyo bigufasha kwirinda
kugura ibintu ujyendeye kumarangamutima.

300
00:17:37,742 --> 00:17:42,912
Murabizi? abantu biga,
ibijyanye no kugura no kumenyekanisha ibintu

301
00:17:42,912 --> 00:17:49,717
Bazi byinshi
kubijyanye n'amarangamutima ahobora kuza

302
00:17:49,717 --> 00:17:51,077
Uramutse uguze ikintu.

303
00:17:51,077 --> 00:17:52,258
Byatuma wumva umerewe neza.

304
00:17:52,258 --> 00:17:56,067
Byagabanya kumva utishimye, cyangwa nibindi.

305
00:17:56,067 --> 00:17:59,349
Bishobora kuzamura amarangamutima, ni bindi wifuza gukora.

306
00:17:59,349 --> 00:18:03,748
Nka Rwiyemezamirimo ucunga amafranga yawe.

307
00:18:03,748 --> 00:18:06,732
Ugomba kwirinda amarangamutima mu kugura, kandi ugatekereza.

308
00:18:06,732 --> 00:18:09,224
Uti, nshobora kubaho ibi bidahari?

309
00:18:09,224 --> 00:18:11,134
Ese nshobora kuba mbiretse mu gihe runaka.

310
00:18:11,134 --> 00:18:13,999
nkareba kubindi byihutirwa, mukigwi kibi??

311
00:18:14,707 --> 00:18:18,658
Wabiha undi Rwiyemezamirimo akabikora igihe biri ngombwa, kumirimo imwe nimwe,

312
00:18:19,358 --> 00:18:20,999
aho kugirango ushake undi wabikora,

313
00:18:20,999 --> 00:18:24,087
birashoboka ko wabiha undi muntu wo kubikora,

314
00:18:24,087 --> 00:18:27,633
nanone ukamuhemba kubyo yakoze, bitandukanye no kumuha umushahara.

315
00:18:27,633 --> 00:18:30,147
Ntago ukeneye kwikururira ibitwara amafranga byinshi.

316
00:18:30,147 --> 00:18:31,378
Ukwiye kwitonda. 

317
00:18:31,378 --> 00:18:34,872
Hari icyo ukwiye kumenya iyo watanze ibintu hirya ngo babigukorere,

318
00:18:34,872 --> 00:18:37,133
ntago ukeneye gukoresha hirya ibintu,

319
00:18:37,133 --> 00:18:40,356
bifite ububasha mugukurura abakiriya bawe.

320
00:18:40,356 --> 00:18:41,992
Ibi tuzabivugaho cyane mu cyumweru gitaha,

321
00:18:41,992 --> 00:18:46,995
gusa ntukwiye gukoresha ibintu kuwabihimbye,

322
00:18:46,995 --> 00:18:49,993
kandi uzi neza gukora ibyo ushaka gukora.

323
00:18:49,993 --> 00:18:51,732
Aha ukeneye kubizanamo umuntu, 

324
00:18:51,732 --> 00:18:53,608
hanyuma akagukkorera.

325
00:18:53,608 --> 00:18:57,570
Kurundi ruhande, niba ari serivice ushaka, ukwiye,

326
00:18:57,570 --> 00:19:00,323
kwita kumuntu ugomba ukoherereza amapaki,

327
00:19:00,323 --> 00:19:07,125
kuko byo ntibyaba bibi igihe bigiye hanze

328
00:19:07,125 --> 00:19:09,796
kumugaragaro mu baturage.

329
00:19:09,796 --> 00:19:11,376
Hariye, birakwiye ko,

330
00:19:11,376 --> 00:19:15,781
naho ushaka umukozi, urugero, uwohereza amapaki cyangwa ibindi.

331
00:19:17,022 --> 00:19:19,657
Gabanya guhomba kwawe. Wirenze urugero. Bishatse kuvuga iki?

332
00:19:19,657 --> 00:19:23,638
Bishatse kuvuga ko  igihe wabonye akazi kawe kamaze kugaragara, uba wabonye ibitekerezo,

333
00:19:23,638 --> 00:19:26,176
ugira umuntu ugusaba kwagura ibicururuzwa byawe,

334
00:19:26,176 --> 00:19:29,696
cyangwa ufite ikindi gitekerezo cyangwa ikintu gishya, 

335
00:19:29,696 --> 00:19:32,024
ntukeneye kugumana abatsindwa,

336
00:19:32,024 --> 00:19:33,482
ngo ukomeze ubatangeho amafranga.

337
00:19:33,482 --> 00:19:37,563
Ubwo rero, ufata ikemezo mukugabanya guhomba,

338
00:19:37,563 --> 00:19:39,418
kugirango udakomeza gutanga amafranga,

339
00:19:39,418 --> 00:19:41,948
kubintu bitazazana amfranga.

340
00:19:42,357 --> 00:19:45,568
Nanone kandi, nkuwahanze igikorwa, yego,

341
00:19:45,568 --> 00:19:47,883
ushobora kugabanya umushahara wawe.

342
00:19:47,883 --> 00:19:53,443
Bishobora kuba bidashimishije cyane, gusa birakwiye ko ushobora kubikora,

343
00:19:53,953 --> 00:19:56,206
mbere yuko ugabanya umushahara wabandi-

344
00:19:56,206 --> 00:20:00,734
umwe nkikimetso, babiri, kongera akanyamuneza, kugirango amafranga asohoka agabanuke.

345
00:20:01,214 --> 00:20:02,610
Tegura gutera teranya amafranga.

346
00:20:02,610 --> 00:20:05,250
Icyo gihe, uraba uteganyije,

347
00:20:05,250 --> 00:20:08,020
nushaka kureba nkuko twabivuze mbere,

348
00:20:08,020 --> 00:20:10,614
uraba udashaka kugera hahantu habi,

349
00:20:10,614 --> 00:20:13,755
hamezi atandatu cyangwa munsi yigihe gisigaye.

350
00:20:13,755 --> 00:20:15,631
mbere y'uko amafaranga agushirana.

351
00:20:15,631 --> 00:20:18,258
Ubwo rero, ukeneye gutegura iterateranya ryamafranga neza,

352
00:20:18,258 --> 00:20:23,211
kandi ugatangira kureba igihe uyakeneye bidakabije,

353
00:20:23,211 --> 00:20:25,024
igihe utayacyeneye cyane.

354
00:20:25,024 --> 00:20:29,107
Ikindi, birumvikana ko ugerageza gufata uko amafranga akomeza kwinjira. 

355
00:20:29,107 --> 00:20:30,738
Niba wabona ukuntu abantu biyandikisha

356
00:20:30,738 --> 00:20:33,347
Aho abantu baba bishyura buri gihe,

357
00:20:33,347 --> 00:20:35,037
cyangwa abakiriya bawe bari kwishyura--

358
00:20:35,037 --> 00:20:37,229
Niba bidakunze ko biba 
kubantu bose

359
00:20:37,229 --> 00:20:41,503
Bishobora kuba ari ama companyi amwe,
aho acuruzanya hagati yayo

360
00:20:41,503 --> 00:20:44,460
Bakaba ari abakiriya bawe
kandi bakaba bahora bishyura, mubihe bisubiramo

361
00:20:44,460 --> 00:20:47,394
bitandukanye no kuba wagurisha ikintu
bigahita birangira.

362
00:20:47,394 --> 00:20:52,830
Ibyo nibyo bizakubera byiza,
ndetse n'uburyo amafaraga ajyenda,

363
00:20:52,830 --> 00:20:55,230
Bizanakubera byiza kandi,
mumicungire y'amafaranga.

364
00:20:55,230 --> 00:20:56,926
Noneho, kugira ama konti atandukanye.

365
00:20:56,926 --> 00:20:58,639
Ubu rwose ukeneye kubikora.

366
00:20:58,639 --> 00:21:01,658
Ntago ukeneye kujyita konti ya banki ngo ukore ibi,

367
00:21:01,658 --> 00:21:04,310
Ukeneye kubika 
amafaranga ya companyi ahatandukanye

368
00:21:04,310 --> 00:21:07,046
n'amafaranga yawe bwite,
ndetse niba ufite konti ya banki,

369
00:21:07,046 --> 00:21:09,776
Ukeneye kujyira 
konti ya companyi

370
00:21:09,776 --> 00:21:11,679
Itandukanye n'iyawe bwite.

371
00:21:11,679 --> 00:21:13,191
Niba ufite ikarita y'inguzanyo
ukeneye kujyira

372
00:21:13,191 --> 00:21:16,021
ikarita y'inguzanyo ya komapanyi itandukanye,
n'iyawe bwite.

373
00:21:16,021 --> 00:21:19,999
Kuko ntago ushaka
kugera aho

374
00:21:19,999 --> 00:21:24,549
Uguza amafaranga
muri kompanyi yawe, murabizi?

375
00:21:24,782 --> 00:21:27,477
wenda hari igihe cyizagera,
ahantu runaka

376
00:21:27,477 --> 00:21:31,024
aho ukeneye amafaranga make
hanyuma ukavuga,

377
00:21:31,024 --> 00:21:34,755
"Oh, sinzi neza niba ibi--

378
00:21:34,755 --> 00:21:36,998
Yego, ntacyo bitwaye,
n'ubundi yose ni amafaranga yanjye."

379
00:21:36,998 --> 00:21:40,400
Nyuma y'aho hantu ni ahantu habi,

380
00:21:40,400 --> 00:21:42,867
mbere y'uko utangira gukoresha 
amafaranga ya kompanyi menshi.

381
00:21:42,867 --> 00:21:44,775
Rero ni byiza kubireka bitandukanye,

382
00:21:44,775 --> 00:21:47,603
Kuburyo niba ugiye kwitiza amafaranga
uyakuye muri kompanyi yawe

383
00:21:47,603 --> 00:21:49,055
Uba ubibona neza ko aribyo uri gukora

384
00:21:49,055 --> 00:21:51,215
ndetse ukaba wakwiyendikira n'agapapuro

385
00:21:51,215 --> 00:21:53,217
ko ugomba kwiyishyura ushyizeho n'inyungu

386
00:21:53,217 --> 00:21:56,082
Ariko byibuza
uri kwandika mubitabo byawe

387
00:21:56,082 --> 00:21:58,196
n'imitungo yawe yindi, bitandukanye

388
00:21:58,196 --> 00:22:02,751
n'ibya companyi yawe
ndetse na gahunda z'amafaranga yawe bwite.

389
00:22:02,751 --> 00:22:06,371
Nonaha, ngiye 
kuba ngiye kuruhande ho gato

390
00:22:06,371 --> 00:22:09,757
uko nabonye ko tutabivuzeho
kujyeza ubu

391
00:22:11,107 --> 00:22:13,919
Kujyira konti zitandukanye 
ni umuco mwiza.

392
00:22:13,919 --> 00:22:16,775
Bituma utanyereza umutungo.

393
00:22:16,775 --> 00:22:19,929
Ariko ntibivuga ko bizakurinda

394
00:22:19,929 --> 00:22:22,443
Gukora ibindi usabwa n'amategeko,
bityo ugomba kwitonda hano.

395
00:22:22,443 --> 00:22:26,613
Ngiye gusa 
n'utandukira ho gato ariko

396
00:22:26,613 --> 00:22:29,838
Ibuka ko niba
Igihe cyimwe

397
00:22:29,838 --> 00:22:31,898
niba ufite icyibazo cy'amadeni

398
00:22:31,898 --> 00:22:35,075
ukwiye gutekereza ku
uburyo bishobora kujyira ingaruka

399
00:22:35,075 --> 00:22:37,379
ku mitungo yawe bwite

400
00:22:37,509 --> 00:22:40,781
Ndetsse n'uburyo ukoramo ishoramari
buzagira uruhare runini muri byo

401
00:22:40,781 --> 00:22:42,847
Reka tubivugeho 
mu masegonda macye

402
00:22:42,847 --> 00:22:45,386
Reka tuvuge gacye ku madeni
n'uburyo bw'imikorere.

403
00:22:45,386 --> 00:22:50,266
Mubihugu byinshi haba
Gutandukanya

404
00:22:50,266 --> 00:22:54,961
Hagati y'uburyo bw'imikorere
bikarengera ba nyiri za kompanyi

405
00:22:54,961 --> 00:22:59,159
n'amadeni afitwe
na za kompanyi zabo.

406
00:22:59,159 --> 00:23:01,989
Hakaba n'izitarengera
nyir'umushinga, cyangwa ba nyirawo.

407
00:23:01,989 --> 00:23:04,539
Hariho ibyiciro bibiri
by''ingenzi hano.

408
00:23:04,539 --> 00:23:06,887
Ibyo rero bitandukana
igihugu ukwacyo icyindi ukwacyo,

409
00:23:06,887 --> 00:23:11,885
Ni ngombwa ko usobanukirwa

410
00:23:11,885 --> 00:23:15,115
Amategko yo mu gihugu cyawe.

411
00:23:15,115 --> 00:23:17,816
Ariko niba uri gutekereza
muri rusange--

412
00:23:17,816 --> 00:23:18,994
Ibyiciro bibiri by'ingezi.

413
00:23:18,994 --> 00:23:22,901
Icyambere ni igihe 
ideni ritagira aho rigarukira

414
00:23:23,581 --> 00:23:26,807
Icyindi ni igihe
ideni rifite aho rigarukira.

415
00:23:26,807 --> 00:23:28,073
Ibyo rero bisobanuye iki?

416
00:23:28,073 --> 00:23:31,669
Ideni ni igihe ufite inshingano

417
00:23:31,669 --> 00:23:35,007
Ko gikorwa cyose kompanyi yawe ikora.

418
00:23:35,738 --> 00:23:39,528
Niba ucuruza ibicuruzwa
hanyuma bikajyira uwo bigiraho ingaruka mbi,

419
00:23:39,528 --> 00:23:46,900
Ubwo ukaba ufite inshingano
zo kwishyura bimwe mubyangijwe

420
00:23:47,309 --> 00:23:49,994
K'umuntu byakomerekeje.

421
00:23:49,994 --> 00:23:53,024
Niba kompanyi yawe yatumye umuntu--

422
00:23:54,504 --> 00:23:57,874
bitewe n'uburangare cyangwa ikindi
atakaza amafaranga ye,

423
00:23:57,874 --> 00:24:01,945
wowe ubwawe ukaba ufite inshingano

424
00:24:01,945 --> 00:24:04,612
zo kwishyura uwo muntu ibyangiritse

425
00:24:04,612 --> 00:24:08,042
Iyo niyo mfuruka turi kureberamo ideni hano,

426
00:24:08,042 --> 00:24:11,989
Hanyuma icyo tujyiye gukora,
tujyiye kujyira ibyo dutandukanya.

427
00:24:11,989 --> 00:24:13,406
Bibiri bya mbere kuri uru rutonde nibyo

428
00:24:13,406 --> 00:24:16,542
Ideni ryawe,
ritagira aho rigarukira,

429
00:24:16,542 --> 00:24:19,496
Cyangwa se tuvuge ko rigarukira,
ku mitungo yawe bwite

430
00:24:20,423 --> 00:24:24,155
Umushinga w'umuntu ku giti cye,
ni igihe uri mu ishoramari ntawe mufatanyije.

431
00:24:24,928 --> 00:24:30,782
Na kompanyi yawe ikaba ari nkaho
ari wowe ubwawe.

432
00:24:31,191 --> 00:24:34,319
Ikaba ri iyawe wenyine
ibyo nibyo twita ko ari iyawe ku giti cyawe

433
00:24:34,319 --> 00:24:36,603
ikibaye cyose 
muri kompanyi

434
00:24:36,603 --> 00:24:40,160
Cyikajyira ingaruka kuri wowe ubwawe nk'umuntu umwe

435
00:24:40,160 --> 00:24:42,104
Hashobora kubaho rero n'ishyirahamwe

436
00:24:42,104 --> 00:24:44,068
mu ma shyirahamwe amwe bajyira amadeni agira aho agarukira;

437
00:24:44,068 --> 00:24:46,811
Ahandi ugasanga atagira aho agarukira.

438
00:24:47,969 --> 00:24:50,828
amashyirahamwe menshi ariko
usanga afite amadeni atajyira aho agarukira,

439
00:24:50,828 --> 00:24:57,028
Aho abishyize hamwe bose
basangira inshingano z'ikibazo icyo aricyo cyose

440
00:24:57,028 --> 00:24:59,956
Ibyo biba muma shyirahamwe,

441
00:24:59,956 --> 00:25:02,471
Ariko ntago yose, rero mwite kubisobanuro birambuye.

442
00:25:03,551 --> 00:25:06,644
Tukajyira rero n'izo zitwa
kompanyi z'amadeni agira aho agarukira.

443
00:25:06,774 --> 00:25:10,394
abantu bakunze kuzita mucyongereza LLCs
icyo ibyo bivuga rero 

444
00:25:10,394 --> 00:25:15,076
Ni uko banyirazo baba basa n'abatandukanye

445
00:25:15,076 --> 00:25:18,706
n'igikorwa cyose kompanyi yakora.

446
00:25:18,706 --> 00:25:20,343
Kompanyi ishobora kuba ifite imitungo yayo,

447
00:25:20,343 --> 00:25:25,203
Iyo mitungo,
ikaba ariyo yafatirwa

448
00:25:25,203 --> 00:25:27,257
Hagize icyibazo icyo ari cyo cyose cyivuka

449
00:25:27,257 --> 00:25:30,247
Kompanyi yatumye hari ibintu by'umuntu byangirika.

450
00:25:30,247 --> 00:25:36,758
Ariko, imitungo ya banyirayo ikaba itavangwa
n'imitungo ya kompanyi

451
00:25:36,758 --> 00:25:39,277
mugikorwa icyo ari cyo cyose cyijyanye n'amategeko.

452
00:25:39,277 --> 00:25:41,701
Kandi akenshi, ibihugu byinshi
batandukanya

453
00:25:41,701 --> 00:25:45,749
za LLCs ntoya n'inini

454
00:25:47,289 --> 00:25:49,909
Intoya
bisobanuye ifite munsi, ya

455
