Umubare runaka w'abishyize hamwe.
20, 50, cyangwa abandi.

456
00:25:56,876 --> 00:26:00,915
Hanyuma inini zika zifite,
umubare munini w'abafatanya bikorwa,

457
00:26:01,715 --> 00:26:04,454
Ibyo abenshi bita,
umushinga wa rusange.

458
00:26:04,917 --> 00:26:10,698
Muri icyo gihe, ba nyir'umushinga
ntago bahabwa inshingano

459
00:26:10,698 --> 00:26:13,552
kubyo kompanyi yabo yakora.

460
00:26:14,619 --> 00:26:16,491
none ni irihe tandukaniro
riri hagati y'ubu buryo bwose?

461
00:26:16,491 --> 00:26:21,548
Yego, izi ziri ahabanza 
kuri uru rutonde

462
00:26:21,548 --> 00:26:24,028
Ziroroshye gushinga.

463
00:26:24,028 --> 00:26:26,488
Ntamafaranga menshi bitwara, niba hari na macye.

464
00:26:27,218 --> 00:26:30,420
Ibintu byo ku giti cy'umntu
bitwara amafaranga hafi ya ntayo kubitangiza.

465
00:26:32,420 --> 00:26:35,755
mughe ubufatanye bunini
bitwara menshi--

466
00:26:35,755 --> 00:26:37,792
Tutavuze n'ingano y'igishoro 
Uba ukeneye

467
00:26:37,792 --> 00:26:40,118
kujyirango ube wakora ubufatanye bunini

468
00:26:40,118 --> 00:26:43,241
hari n'ibindi bitwara amafaranga byinshi.

469
00:26:43,241 --> 00:26:48,695
Amafaranga ajyenda mu icungamari,
amafaranga musabwa n'amategeko n'ibindi

470
00:26:50,905 --> 00:26:54,699
Gukora kugiti cyawe--
biroroshye cyaane ndetse birahendutse gutangiza

471
