naho iby'ubufatanye bunini
birahenze cyane gutangiza, ndetse no gukora.

472
00:27:00,945 --> 00:27:03,044
Ariko kurundi ruhande, biba bihwanye,

473
00:27:03,044 --> 00:27:06,741
kubera ko ibyo kugiti cyawe
biba bifite amadeni atagira aho agarukira,

474
00:27:06,741 --> 00:27:10,732
Hanyuma ukaba uzagomba,
gufata inshingano

475
00:27:10,732 --> 00:27:13,976
Igikorwa cyose cya kompanyi yawe,
mugihe mubufatanye bunini,

476
00:27:13,976 --> 00:27:17,494
Uratandukanye cyane--
uretse mubihe bimwe

477
00:27:17,494 --> 00:27:19,441
Nabyo muri icyi gihe
bitoroshye kugeramo--

478
00:27:19,441 --> 00:27:22,847
Ntago waryozwa,
ibyo kompanyi yakora.

479
00:27:23,632 --> 00:27:25,776
Tukivuga kuri ibyo, 
reka mbigarukeho hano--

480
00:27:25,776 --> 00:27:29,599
Sindi kubagira inama
muby'amategeko cg ubukungu

481
00:27:29,599 --> 00:27:34,286
Mugomba kureba mu bihugu byanyu
Amategeko

482
00:27:34,286 --> 00:27:38,426
agenga iby'amadeni n'uburyo bw'imikorere
bishobora kuba bihinduka,

483
00:27:38,426 --> 00:27:40,745
Ndetse hatitawe kubintu mvuga hano,

484
00:27:40,745 --> 00:27:44,950
Buri gihugu kigira amategeko yacyo
kubijyanye n'amadeni n'inshingano

485
00:27:44,950 --> 00:27:47,531
