ibyo bintu,

486
00:27:47,531 --> 00:27:51,114
cyane cyane niba uri gushinga
ibicuruzwa cyangwa serivisi

487
00:27:51,114 --> 00:27:58,018
Bishobora kujyira rimwe na rimwe
icyintu byakwangiza,

488
00:27:59,100 --> 00:28:00,924
Icyo cyaba ari cyo cyose.

489
00:28:00,924 --> 00:28:03,767
Rero sindi kubabwira ibyo mugomba gukora.
ndikubabwira gusa

490
00:28:03,767 --> 00:28:08,969
Ibyo abantu batekerezaho
iyo bari gutekereza ku ma deni n'inshingano,

491
00:28:09,165 --> 00:28:11,976
Reka twisubirire kuma konti noneho.

492
00:28:12,397 --> 00:28:15,378
Mubikorwa, guhitamo banki.

493
00:28:17,080 --> 00:28:22,159
Ni ingenzi, iyo bishoboka,
kuba ukorana na banki

494
00:28:22,159 --> 00:28:24,741
cyangwa ibigo by'imari
iyo ufite icyigo cy'ubucuruzi.

495
00:28:26,121 --> 00:28:29,639
Ubwo rero icyintu cya mbere
ushobora gutekerezaho

496
00:28:29,639 --> 00:28:32,027
Ni ukujyira konti muri banki

497
00:28:32,027 --> 00:28:34,704
Cyangwa ubundi buryo bwo kuzigama,

498
00:28:34,704 --> 00:28:36,164
Tuzakuvugaho nyuma gato.

499
00:28:36,164 --> 00:28:38,180
Niba igiye kuba banki igaragara rero,

500
00:28:38,180 --> 00:28:39,928
Reka dutekereze kubintu bikurikira:

501
00:28:39,928 --> 00:28:43,324
Ni gute iyo banki ikorohereza?

502
00:28:44,044 --> 00:28:46,743
Iri amagana he 
ugereranyije n'aho utuye,

503
00:28:47,663 --> 00:28:49,979
cyangwa aho ukorera n'ibindi?

504
00:28:49,979 --> 00:28:52,689
Hari ibintu byatuma utahajyera byoroshye?

505
00:28:52,689 --> 00:28:55,619
Amabanki amwe, wabyemera cyangwa utabyemera
aba aca amafaranga menshi

506
00:28:55,619 --> 00:28:59,266
Iyo utagiye ku ishami rikwegereye
wafungurijeho konti

507
00:28:59,684 --> 00:29:02,114
Ibyo bishobora kuba wowe ntacyo bigutwaye,

508
00:29:02,114 --> 00:29:04,814
Ariko ushobora gukenera gukorana na banki,

509
00:29:04,814 --> 00:29:06,548
mu mashami menshi ya banki imwe,

510
00:29:06,548 --> 00:29:08,798
Muri icyo gihe rero
ntabwo uba ukeneye imbogamizi nk'izo.

511
00:29:09,428 --> 00:29:14,592
Kugira umuntu muhura wa nyawe,
atari ahantu uhamagara gusa

512
00:29:14,592 --> 00:29:18,907
ahubwo umuntu uri
ushinzwe kwakira abakiriya

513
00:29:19,092 --> 00:29:21,883
kuri banki, umuntu wa nyawe,
uzi amazina ye,

514
00:29:21,883 --> 00:29:24,792
mushobora kuganira,
nabyo ni akarusho.

515
00:29:25,155 --> 00:29:28,139
ndey=tse n'igihe bitwara,
kugira ngo ufunguze konti,

516
00:29:28,139 --> 00:29:33,522
Gishobora kuba cyiri hagati y'iminota micye
n'amezi macye,

517
00:29:33,522 --> 00:29:36,771
bitewe na banki, igihugu, n'ibindi, etc.

518
00:29:36,771 --> 00:29:38,689
Ukeneye kandi,
kugenda genda mo gacye,

519
00:29:38,689 --> 00:29:40,812
