icyintu cyikoroheye kurushaho.

520
00:29:40,812 --> 00:29:43,226
Ese baguha uburyo bwo gukorana nabo wifashishije ikoranabuhanga?

521
00:29:43,226 --> 00:29:44,584
Icyo turaza kukivugaho gatoya,
mukanya gato,

522
00:29:44,584 --> 00:29:48,640
