Mbese, muyandi magambo, niba wumvaa-
niba ari ubukungu bushingiye kuri sheki

527
00:30:02,888 --> 00:30:05,628
Niwandika sheki,
bizatwara igihe cyingana gute

528
00:30:05,628 --> 00:30:07,583
Kugirango ayo mafaranga abe yabonetse?

529
00:30:07,583 --> 00:30:10,032
Umuntu ni akwandikira sheki
ukayishyira kuri banki,

530
00:30:10,032 --> 00:30:12,788
