aho baguca macye, mukureba ayo usigaje, ayo baca kuri sheki,

536
00:30:30,858 --> 00:30:33,682
Inyungu, kukurinda kujya munsi ya zeru kuri konti--

537
00:30:33,682 --> 00:30:37,318
