560
00:31:53,168 --> 00:31:56,474
Kugirango ubashe gukorana nabo kuri murandasi,
mbese no kuri telefone yawe.

561
00:31:56,474 --> 00:32:01,164
Itandukaniro rihari ni uko,
aba ari banki ya nyayo ibyihishe inyuma.

562
00:32:02,604 --> 00:32:05,831
Ukurikije amategeko amwe
kubijyanye n'inguzanyo

563
00:32:05,831 --> 00:32:09,743
Haba hari akenshi uburyo
bw'ubwishingizi mu kubitsa, n'ibindi.

564
00:32:09,743 --> 00:32:14,166
Rero hari gukorana na banki,
nyine nk'uko bisanzwe,

565
00:32:14,166 --> 00:32:17,252
Ujyereranije no gukoresha ikoranabuhanga mukwishyura

566
00:32:17,252 --> 00:32:19,870
Ibyo abantu bita kandi
gutanga amafaranga biciye mu ikoranabuhanga

567
00:32:19,870 --> 00:32:22,877
cyangwa uburyo bwo kugufasha amafaranga--
muyandi magambo,

568
00:32:22,877 --> 00:32:25,831
Ni nk'uburyo bwa paypay,

569
00:32:25,831 --> 00:32:29,692
Aho wowe,
udakora kumafaranga

570
00:32:29,692 --> 00:32:33,896
mujyihe cyo kuyahererekanya,
ukaba utayakoraho--

571
00:32:34,786 --> 00:32:38,007
Bakaba bataguha inyungu kumafaranga, 
urugero,

572
00:32:38,007 --> 00:32:40,484
Kandi bakaba batanaguriza abantu amafaranga.

573
00:32:40,484 --> 00:32:44,749
Rero ntago iba ari banki ya nyayo,
mubihugu byinshi rero--

574
00:32:44,749 --> 00:32:48,440
Ni ibyo 
kugufasha amafaranga gusa

575
00:32:48,440 --> 00:32:50,091
Bigakoreshwa ikoranabuhanga

576
00:32:50,091 --> 00:32:51,793
Hari n'icyindi cyiciro cya gatatu

577
00:32:51,793 --> 00:32:54,246
y'uburyo bwa mobile money "mobayilomani"
cyangwa kubika gaciro k'amafaranga,

578
00:32:54,246 --> 00:32:56,046
Bitewe n'icyo ari cyo.

579
00:32:58,596 --> 00:33:00,286
Aha ni aho kenshi na kenshi,

580
00:33:00,286 --> 00:33:03,761
Wishyura mebre serivisi zimwe na zimwe
tuvuge nka serivisi ya telecom,

581
00:33:03,761 --> 00:33:06,379
Iyo serivisi ya telecom
ikaba ikorana na telefoni yawe.

582
00:33:06,379 --> 00:33:08,071
Ndakoresha iminota runaka 
kuri telefoni yanjye

583
00:33:08,071 --> 00:33:09,630
Ndishyura,
amafaranga runaka,

584
00:33:09,630 --> 00:33:13,382
Hanyuma kompanyi ya telefoni,
ibike ayo mafaranga

585
00:33:13,382 --> 00:33:18,011
Iyakubikire kuri konti
aho ushobora kuyakoresha

586
00:33:18,011 --> 00:33:21,968
Wishyura undi munti
cyangwa waira amafaranga avuye kuwundi muntu.

587
00:33:21,968 --> 00:33:26,298
Ibi byafunguye isi nshya,
yo kuhana amafaranga hadakoreshejwe kashi

588
00:33:26,298 --> 00:33:30,893
Binafungurira inzira abakiriya badakoresha ama banki.

589
00:33:30,893 --> 00:33:32,472
abakiriya ubusanzwe batashoboraga

590
00:33:32,472 --> 00:33:36,201
Kuba bafite konti muri banki, ikarita y'inguzanyo
bafite gusa telefoni zigendanwa.

591
00:33:36,201 --> 00:33:38,457
Ntago zigomba kuba ari serivisi za telecom gusa,

592
00:33:38,457 --> 00:33:42,131
byanaba ubwoko bwose bwo kubika agaciro k'amafaranga,
aho bishoboka.

593
00:33:42,131 --> 00:33:44,032
hari ubushakashatsi,
butandukanye buri gukorwa

594
00:33:44,032 --> 00:33:49,714
mu isi yose kuri ubu,
kuburyo bwo kubika agaciro k'amafaranga.

595
00:33:49,714 --> 00:33:52,131
Ariko ako ni akantu k'ibanze,
inyuma ya mobile money

596
00:33:52,131 --> 00:33:55,841
Hanyuma waba ukeneye amafaranga cyane,
ukajya ahantu runaka,

597
00:33:55,841 --> 00:34:01,302
ahantu runaka hazwi
aho wakohereza ubutumwa

598
00:34:01,302 --> 00:34:04,065
Ku muntu, uwo muntu nawe 
akaguha amafaranga kashi

599
00:34:04,465 --> 00:34:05,760
ahongaho ako kanya.

600
00:34:05,760 --> 00:34:07,667
Rero bishobora guhindurwamo amafaranga

601
00:34:07,667 --> 00:34:10,204
Cyangwa bikaguma nk'agaciro kabitsemo

602
00:34:10,204 --> 00:34:12,802
ukaba wayakoresha uko ubishaka.

603
00:34:12,802 --> 00:34:14,834
Icyibazo cyimwe gusa ukwiye kubaza

604
00:34:14,834 --> 00:34:18,630
Mugihe nk''icyo cy'umuntu k'uwundi ni
ese agaciro kari hehe?

605
00:34:19,520 --> 00:34:22,109
Ese ni muri telefoni yawe?

606
00:34:22,109 --> 00:34:23,991
Muri telefoni yawe--
niba umuntu akwibye telefoni,

607
00:34:23,991 --> 00:34:25,468
amafaranga yawe yose arayatwara?

608
00:34:25,468 --> 00:34:27,837
Cyangwa ari kuri konti
ahantu runaka,

609
00:34:27,837 --> 00:34:30,043
Aho ukeneye umubare w'ibanga,
kujyirango ube wayabikuza,

610
00:34:30,043 --> 00:34:33,193
kuburyo niyo wabura telefoni,
ukomeza kuba wagumana amafaranga yawe,

611
00:34:33,193 --> 00:34:36,054
Ugahindura telefoni,
hanyuma ukagumana uburyo bwo kujyera kuri iyo konti.

612
00:34:36,054 --> 00:34:37,909
Rero ugomba kwibaza,

613
00:34:37,909 --> 00:34:39,818
niba uri gutekereza kuri ibyo bintu,

614
00:34:39,818 --> 00:34:41,714
Uti ese agaciro kaba kari hehe?

615
00:34:41,714 --> 00:34:45,007
Ese ni muri chip iri ku ikarita
cyangwa ni ahandi hantu kure?

616
00:34:45,007 --> 00:34:48,349
niba ari ahandi hantu kure, rero ugomba kuba ufite,
uburyo bwo guhura naho

617
00:34:48,349 --> 00:34:52,554
Ukabasha kohereza no kwakira amafaranga.

618
00:34:53,493 --> 00:34:56,128
Bizana n'ikindi kibazo 
kubijyanye n'ubwishingizi.

619
00:34:56,128 --> 00:35:00,242
Mubihugu byinshi
konti za banki ziba zishinganye,

620
00:35:00,242 --> 00:35:03,027
Bisobanuye ko niba banki
iramutse ifunze imiryango,

621
00:35:03,027 --> 00:35:08,914
Guverinoma isezeranya wishyura
 akenshi, amafaranga yose

622
00:35:08,914 --> 00:35:11,101
y'abantu babitsamo-- ikabishyura.

623
00:35:12,221 --> 00:35:16,207
Ikibazo kindi ugomba kubaza 
muri ubu buryo bw'umuntu k'uwundi

624
00:35:16,207 --> 00:35:17,752
Ni ese ayo mafaranga nayo arashinganye?

625
00:35:17,752 --> 00:35:21,583
Niba adashinganye ntacyo, ariko nanone
ntago washyira amafaranga yose

626
00:35:22,533 --> 00:35:27,026
muburyo bw'umuntu k'uwundi
bw'agaciro k'amafaranga.

627
00:35:27,094 --> 00:35:30,332
NI ibintu bicye watekerezaho,
hano, ariko muri rusange

628
00:35:30,332 --> 00:35:33,362
Navugako inyungu

629
00:35:33,362 --> 00:35:37,692
Zo kwakira no gutanga amafaranga hakoreshejwe ikoranabuhanga

630
00:35:37,692 --> 00:35:42,885
Ziruta kure ingaruka mbi
zo gutanga no kwakira amafaranga hakoreshejwe ikoranabuhanga.
